[6] Perm
Date: 3 Nov 2006
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Ami Tass [translated by Mod NR, edited]
<http://www.ami-tass.ru/article/16269.html>

13 people died in Perm, 247 are diagnosed with toxic hepatitis
-----------------------------------------------
According to Olga Shutova (chief of Rospotrebnadzor), the scope of
alcohol poisoning is expanding to include the cities of Perm, Kungur,
Chaykovskiy, Chusovoy, Solikamsk, and Krasnokamsk.
[Map at http://www.lovesbridge.com/Images/perm-cis-map.gif>]
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
